==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: macrocephaly
<hw>macrocephaly</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>THe condition of having an
unusually large head; it differs from <contr>hydrocephalus</contr>
because there is no increase intracranial pressure and the overgrowth is
symmetrical.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> megacephaly, megalocephaly.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Macrocheira</ent>⟦br⟧
